00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:42.359
When I come back,

00:01:42.879 --> 00:01:44.760
I'll tell everyone about us.

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:46.680
We'll never be apart again.

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:47.599
All right.

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:49.840
Two years will pass quickly.

00:01:50.959 --> 00:01:52.000
Wait for me to return.

00:02:01.239 --> 00:02:04.799
Come here.

00:02:18.610 --> 00:02:19.800
- Second Young Master.
- Second Young Master.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:21.360
You're looking better by the day, sir.

00:02:21.810 --> 00:02:22.199
Yansheng.

00:02:22.199 --> 00:02:22.660
Grandmother.

00:02:22.919 --> 00:02:23.240
Mother.

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:25.439
My precious son, you're finally home!

00:02:25.439 --> 00:02:26.599
It's been two years.

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:28.199
I've missed you so much!

00:02:30.039 --> 00:02:31.479
My little darling.

00:02:31.479 --> 00:02:32.599
Come, sit down quickly.

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:33.199
Sit down.

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.080
Shiqi.

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:35.560
Yansheng.

00:02:36.639 --> 00:02:37.240
Yunyun.

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:40.240
From now on,

00:02:40.479 --> 00:02:42.039
you can't call her Yunyun anymore.

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:45.319
She's already married to your brother.

00:02:45.319 --> 00:02:46.599
You should call her Sister-in-law.

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:07.199
I...

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.599
I'm going to the bathroom.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:10.879
He's home now.

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.360
Yansheng will be fine.

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:27.000
Didn't you say you'd wait for me?

00:03:27.199 --> 00:03:28.280
What happened?

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:29.759
Why did you suddenly marry my brother?

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:33.439
Why?

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:34.719
Why?

00:03:34.719 --> 00:03:35.599
Gu Yansheng.

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:38.759
I've never liked you.

00:03:41.199 --> 00:03:43.360
The one I want to marry
is the head of the Gu family.

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:45.120
You're not worthy.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:08.319
(Could Fu Yunyun
really have abandoned him so coldly?)

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.120
Who's there?

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:13.800
Scared already?

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:35.959
Psycho.

00:04:38.399 --> 00:04:39.759
(What does "psycho" mean?)

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:40.800
What are you doing here?

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.720
Just taking a walk.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:05.040
Fortunately, we rescued her in time.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.240
The old lady's condition has stabilized.

00:05:07.240 --> 00:05:08.000
However,

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.240
the toxin has affected her brain.

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:09.800
It's likely

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:11.120
she'll remain unconscious for a while.

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:13.040
How long will that be?

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.199
A few days at least,

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:15.399
maybe a few months.

00:05:15.399 --> 00:05:17.000
It depends on her physical condition.

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.600
Once she wakes up,
she should recover fully.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.959
What caused it?

00:05:20.959 --> 00:05:24.120
She probably took
a neurotoxic substance by mistake.

00:05:24.959 --> 00:05:25.720
Thank you, doctor.

00:05:26.279 --> 00:05:26.839
You're welcome.

00:05:31.319 --> 00:05:32.639
I've examined that pill.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.390
There was indeed
something wrong with it.

00:05:35.639 --> 00:05:36.720
I misunderstood you.

00:05:38.519 --> 00:05:39.240
That's great.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.279
I'm just glad Grandmother's safe.

00:05:46.399 --> 00:05:47.240
What's this?

00:05:47.639 --> 00:05:48.480
A handkerchief.

00:05:49.439 --> 00:05:51.240
You never used
this sort of thing before.

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:52.439
Just use it.

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:55.240
Shiqi.

00:05:55.639 --> 00:05:57.920
In life, cry when you want to cry,
laugh when you want to laugh.

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:58.720
Don't restrain yourself.

00:06:00.959 --> 00:06:01.839
Yunyun,

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.480
