00:06:10.639 --> 00:06:11.160
Well,

00:06:11.720 --> 00:06:12.639
if that's all,

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:13.639
I'll take Shiqi back first.

00:06:13.639 --> 00:06:14.399
Stop.

00:06:18.879 --> 00:06:19.959
Tonight,

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:23.279
I'll come to you.

00:06:27.959 --> 00:06:28.480
Let's go.

00:06:49.519 --> 00:06:51.160
How long do I have to stay here?

00:06:52.439 --> 00:06:52.879
Could it be

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.680
that I can never go back?

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:03.120
Do you need something?

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.079
What's the meaning of this?

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.319
We're husband and wife.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.319
Isn't it natural for me
to come to your room?

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:13.120
You...

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:14.639
Don't you dare.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:16.720
We're not truly husband and wife.

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:19.160
And as far as I know,

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.399
